OL,3,CWhy is the Strait of Hormuz so vital
OL,4,Cand how could disruption affect UK
OL,5,Cbills
OL,7,FOil prices have surged as renewed
OL,8,Fconflict between Iran, the US and its
OL,9,Fallies raises fears the war could
OL,10,Frestrict the global flow of crude oil.
OL,12,FSince the US-Israel airstrikes on Iran
OL,13,Fon Saturday, which killed Iran's
OL,14,FSupreme Leader Ayatollah Ali Khamenei
OL,15,Fon Saturday, Iran has effectively shut
OL,16,Fthe strait, threatening, and even
OL,17,Fstriking, vessels that travel through
OL,18,Fthe Strait of Hormuz, a vital shipping
OL,19,Flane for the global economy.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
